<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out this part.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7760f41a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/419/tI/s109">Pub. L. 102–419, title I, § 109</ref>, <date date="1992-10-16">Oct. 16, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/2143">106 Stat. 2143</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/106/356/s2/b">Pub. L. 106–356, § 2(b)</ref>, <date date="2000-10-24">Oct. 24, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/1391">114 Stat. 1391</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
