<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7760f41d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2000—<ref href="/us/pl/106/356">Pub. L. 106–356</ref> struck out “: <i>Provided</i>, That the amount to be appropriated for the operation, development or restoration of non-federally owned properties within the boundaries of the park shall not exceed $200,000” after “this part”.</p>
